      <title>中国建筑商Sunac头部进入第二个离岸重组</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/chinese-builder-sunac-heads-into-second-offshore-restructuring</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Sunac China Holdings Ltd.是最早完成海上重组的主要开发商之一，他正在重新开始这一过程，因为它加入了越来越多的建筑商在长期的财产危机中面临持续的流动性问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-25/chinese-builder-sunac-heads-into-second-offshore-restructuring</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 25 Mar 2025 04:55:54 GMT</pubDate>
